Your case is located at our Potomac Service Center location. Please follow any instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your duplicate notice by April 11, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
